 aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eox1665702644734.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eox1665702644734.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eox1665702644734.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eox1665702644734\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                                      \n #Areas\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Displays the number of areas, or polygons, that comprise this tag.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eox1665702644734__p_d9182e1_d9183e1_d9184e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">#Areas</span> is greater than one, you can select a particular polygon of this tag and do one of the following:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"eox1665702644734__table_d983e1_d984e1_d985e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"eox1665702644734__fig_w216ab1b5b3b1b5b1b1b1_w217ab1b5b3b1b5b1b1_w218ab1b5b3b1b5b1_w219ab1b5b3b1b5_w220ab1b5b3b1_w221ab1b5b3_w222ab1b5_w223ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Icon to separate polygon from its tag\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_map_poly_sep.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Click to separate the polygon from its tag. Uniface gives the separated polygon a new name which you can change.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"eox1665702644734__fig_w224ab1b5b3b1b5b3b1b1_w225ab1b5b3b1b5b3b1_w226ab1b5b3b1b5b3_w227ab1b5b3b1b5_w228ab1b5b3b1_w229ab1b5b3_w230ab1b5_w231ab1\">\n<img alt=\"Icon to separate and delete polygon\" class=\"image\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_map_poly_del.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n Click to separate and delete the polygon in one step.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eox1665702644734__p_d9185e1_d9186e1_d9187e1\">If <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">#Areas</span> is greater than one and you\n         click <img alt=\"Icon to delete polygon and tag\" class=\"image\" id=\"eox1665702644734__image_xjm_mqs_5cc\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/u7_map_tag_del.png?_LANG=enus\"/> to delete the selected polygon, Uniface deletes the polygon and the tag.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527239\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527239\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "#Areas Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 #Areas Displays the number of areas, or polygons, that comprise this tag. If #Areas is greater than one, you can select a particular polygon of this tag and do one of the following: Click to separate the polygon from its tag. Uniface gives the separated polygon a new name which you can change. Click to separate and delete the polygon in one step. If #Areas is greater than one and you click to delete the selected polygon, Uniface deletes the polygon and the tag. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}